:::Vulois:::

::He sees Trinity and smiles::
Vulois: Hello there!  Play? I wish i could. Maybe once i am healed we will 
play.
::He hears Angel Prime's transmission and sees the crowd coming outside::
Vulois: I am Vulois, and this is Thundercracker.  I swear by Primus, we come 
in peace.  We were on a mission to try to stop this war, but things have 
changed around here.  Please, i do not even have a weapon.
